      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid project or reliable point-A-to-point-B transport for someone willing to put in a little work. The engine starts and runs, though it could benefit from a tune-up, and the transmission is functional despite some age-related quirks. Externally, there are several noticeable scratches, some minor dings, and the clear coat is beginning to fade on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery shows significant wear and a few permanent stains, but all major controls and electronics are still operational. It has been a dependable car, but it is now showing its age and is priced to reflect its current state and maintenance needs.",
