    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a mechanical masterpiece. The naturally aspirated 4.0L S65 V8 screams to an 8,400 RPM redline, featuring eight individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response. Mated to a lightning-fast 7-speed M-DCT, the drivetrain delivers seamless power to the rear wheels via a variable M-differential lock. The chassis remains flawlessly rigid, with all bushings and suspension components in factory-new condition. Meticulously maintained with a documented service history, this specimen represents the pinnacle of high-revving atmospheric performance.",
      "price": 47500.0,
