    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true showroom-quality specimen that has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior finish is breathtaking, featuring deep, lustrous paint protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating; there are absolutely no swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in 'time-capsule' condition, with the premium leather upholstery retaining its original matte finish and factory-fresh scent. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the heated seats, functions exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach, supported by a comprehensive folder of service records from the same certified dealership. The engine bay is spotless, showing no signs of fluid seepage or wear. This sale includes all original keys, the factory window sticker, and the complete owner\u2019s manual set. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that bridges the gap between a used car and a brand-new delivery.",
